{
  "texts": [
    "More control over technology: With coding skills, you can better understand how technology works and make changes to suit your needs.",
    "Whether you're automating repetitive tasks, customizing your website, or fixing bugs in a program, coding puts you in control. 5.",
    "Personal satisfaction: Finally, learning to code can provide immense personal satisfaction, as you gain the ability to create something from nothing and tackle complex challenges.",
    "It's an empowering and rewarding skill to have.",
    "Overall, learning to code can provide valuable job opportunities, improved problem-solving and creativity, greater control over technology, and personal satisfaction."
